td.p:
This request for a preliminary ruling concerns the interpretation of Articles 46(2) and 47(1)(d) of Regulation (EEC) No 1408/71 of the Council of 14 June 1971 on the application of social security schemes to employed persons, to self-employed persons and to members of their families moving within the Community, as amended and updated by Council Regulation (EC) No 118/97 of 2 December 1996 (
OJ 1997 L 28, p. 1
), as amended by Council Regulation (EC) No 1606/98 of 29 June 1998 (
OJ 1998 L 209, p. 1
) (‘Regulation No 1408/71’).
